extendedInfo.description: The Walking Dead Fanclub APP is Your number one source for NEWS on The Comic Book/AMC TV series The Walking Dead. This APP is loaded to the brim with access to lots of resources about The Walking Dead including up to date news, comic book and TV show previews and reviews  A back issue checklist and price guide, a library and a summary of all the previous issues and shows Including a cover gallery to The Walking Dead books from all around the world and much, much, more. PLUS we are integrated with Facebook for socializing on the go!A very Special thanks to The Bleeding Rainbow guys, Doc layton, the euge and zombie hero, also our main man Jimmy blue eyes and Rachel from the two cents.com for the excellent walking dead reviews and news that they provide for us!!

reviews.title: Finally a great app for twd fans!
reviews.comment: The application is easy to navigate, looks great and works great, current news weather your a fan of the comic OR the show and its only a buck! If you\'re. A fan of the walking dead this is a must have.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: If you like the walking dead you will love this app
reviews.comment: I usually do not buy or even rate apps but being a fan of the comic and show I had to try this. So glad I did this app has tons of walking dead info I never new. Thanks and 5 $TAR$ all day.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Must have for The Walking Dead Fans!
reviews.comment: I\'m a big fan of their website and it always hosts the latest Walking Dead news!  The website doesn\'t view that great on my phone but using this app does look great!  I love the comic book and TV show and they always have the latest news on both.  Lots of forums to chat with fellow fans.  Only thing missing on this app that is on the website is the Walking Dead featured ebay auctions.  Or maybe I just haven\'t found it yet.
reviews.author: A Google User
